%% Mermaid flowchart describing the prototype topology
flowchart LR
  CLI["CLI"] -->|HTTP POST /api/jobs| API["API Service"]
  CLI -->|HTTP GET /api/jobs| API
  API -->|insert/query| MySQLQueue[(MySQL Queue)]
  Worker["Worker Service"] -->|poll queued jobs| MySQLQueue
  Worker -->|download backup| S3[(AWS S3<br/>Cross-Account)]
  Worker -->|restore + post-SQL| MySQLTarget[(MySQL 8 Host)]
  Worker -->|emit events| MySQLQueue
  Worker -->|metrics + logs| Observability[(Datadog)]
  API -.->|no AWS/myloader access| NoAPIAccess[API has MySQL only]
  CLI -.->|no AWS/MySQL access| NoCLIAccess[CLI has HTTP only]
  Worker -.->|AWS credentials<br/>via profile| AWSProfile[AWS Profile<br/>+ Parameter Store]
  Worker -.->|no HTTP exposure| NoWorkerHTTP[Worker polls MySQL only]

